replies.body:
If you're up to the challenge, i'd say {{champion:268}} 
He can solo carry entire games if played well enough, and doesn't get banned all the time like {{champion:238}} or{{champion:157}} . You probably won't get bored of him either since he requires so much skill you'll always be learning something new. And he's pretty well off against assassins, especially with {{summoner:3}} . 

Hope this helps!
{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
